Target: An ontology for systems of devices

Comment: A combination of several devices working together to achieve a specific task.
Label: System

Comment: A system of laboratory equipments
Label: Lab equipment system

Comment: A system for filtering liquid or gas in a lab environment
Label: Filtration system

Comment: A system for simulating phenomenon in a lab environement
Label: Simulation System

Comment: A system for diluting solutions in a lab environment
Label: Diltuion system

Comment: A system for managing connected bodies actuated by servos.
Label: Servomechanism system

Comment: A system for managing temperature during calorimetery measurements
Label: Calorimetry cooling system

Comment: A system for doing flow cell -based experiments
Label: Cell stack Integrated system

Comment: A system for observing flame synthesis processes
Label: Flame synthesis diagnostic system

Comment: A system for doing calorimetry experiments
Label: Calorimetry system

Comment: A system for experiments that require burning via exposure to fire
Label: Burner system

Comment: A system for mixing several different solutions or solids into 1 homogeneous mix
Label: Mixing system

Comment: A system for freezing samples while removing moisture from the sample
Label: Freeze-dryer system

Comment: A system for capturing the composition and images of a flame
Label: Flame imaging system

Comment: A system for analysing the properties of a combustion done by an engine
Label: Combustion analysis system

Comment: A system for doing chromatography on a solution.
Label: Chromatography system

Comment: A system for diagnosing the emission of an engine.
Label: Emission diagnostic system

Comment: A system for monitoring medical conditions of a human
Label: Medical monitoring system

Comment: A system for stracking eye movement and focus.
Label: Eye tracking system

Comment: A system for doing and collecting data on an electroencephalogram experiments
Label: EEG system

Comment: A system that monitors heart and respiration conditions by detecting electrical signals in the body
Label: ECG and respiration monitoring system

Comment: A system of computer parts working together as a computer or a computer part
Label: Computer system

Comment: A system that manages the sound output of a computer
Label: Sound system

Comment: A system that manages the visual output of a computer
Label: Display system

Comment: A system that manages the global positioning of a device
Label: GPS system

Comment: A system that provides video recordings in a closed circuit environment
Label: CCTV system

Comment: A relation that tells the system is composed of which devices.
Label: composed of

Comment: A relationship that describes the ID assigned to a device.
Label: has ID
